AHB
    master 0 -> Processor
    master 1 -> Debug UART
    master 2 -> JTAG debug
    ------
    slave 1 -> AHB/APB bridge   0x80000000
    slave 2 -> DSU              0x90000000 
    slave 4 -> Test report mod  0x20000000
    slave 5 -> Leon2 memctrl    0x40000000
    slave 6 -> ROM              0x00000000

APB
    slave 0 -> Leon2 memctrl    0x80000000
    slave 1 -> UART             0x80000200
    slave 3 -> timer            0x80000300
    slave 4 -> Debug UART       0x80000700
